Hey <@U026AP8CM> Looks like we didn't get the some of the fonts from Mullen.
We're missing the chalkboard styled fonts. For example, the one used on home page header "We are fearless..." "This is our Beer..."
and also the footer "Welcome To Small Batch..."
There's the possibility that these are custom characters created by Mullen. In that case having a vector version of all the text in those fonts would be very helpful.
so i will ask for chalkboard font, but if it's not a font like klinic that he can pass on, vector version of the text is helpful?
Lastly, can we also ask them for vector versions of all the icons used on the site. For example, the three lines that composed the nav icon, the add to calendar icon, etc.
yep yep! will ask for anything you guys need.
